# Project methodology — track these despite the broad *.md rule above.
# (Vite already excludes .md from the production bundle, so the *.md gitignore
# was over-broad. These files belong in version control so they survive a
# fresh clone / laptop reset.)
#
# Specific paths only — adding `*.md` globs here would pull in pre-existing
# documentation files (e.g. tests_evm/CONTRACT_ANALYSIS.md) that the dev had
# kept local-only. Add new exemptions explicitly as new methodology files
# are created.
!BRAIN.md
!TODO.md
!workflow_rules.md
!tech_learnings.md
!memory/session_*.md
!tests_evm/BANK8_VERIFICATION_*.md
!tools/contract-debug/README.md
!tools/hardhat-deploy/_WHAT_THIS_IS.md
!docs/*.md